{"tid":1507448,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一群熱愛香港足球球迷致香港足球總會公開信","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:20:03.000Z","uid":33508,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6bbdd6f83ad03dffc05117797ae6863b092f99","tid":1507448,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"致香港足球總會的公開信：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群熱愛香港足球，會入場觀賽打氣支持的球迷。近期政府因修訂《逃犯條例》所引起之社會撕裂，有香港市民入境中國內地時受到無理及不必要之審查。得悉貴會有機會決定將香港超級聯賽球隊富力 R&amp;F之來季主場定為中國廣州燕子崗運動場，此舉令一眾香港足球球迷對此感到憂心及不安。<br />\n<br />\n去季，有球員因為政治原因而導致延誤入境中國作賽，這無疑影響賽事的公平性。可惜，貴會沒有相應措施，能防止類似事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n我們重申，除非香港足球總會有能力確保所有職球員及球迷之人身自由和財產安全不會因進入中國境內而受威脅，貴會必須顧及賽事公平，及參與人士安全，運用權力，將富力 R&amp;F主場賽事悉數移回香港進行。否則，我們將會無限期杯葛所有富力R&amp;F之賽事。<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港足球的球迷<br />\n二零一九年八月二十六日<br />\n<br />\n附上反對香港足球總會將富力R&amp;F主場定為中國廣州燕子崗運動場之公眾聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfUc4ssrBB_aoPke6_i_YimRIWpKZJINEQ8O13vn_cR-yEgsA/viewanalytics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfUc4ssrBB_aoPke6_i_YimRIWpKZJINEQ8O13vn_cR-yEgsA%2Fviewanalytics&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY1A4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=8d48ebe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfUc4ssrBB_aoPke6_i_YimRIWpKZJINEQ8O13vn_cR-yEgsA/viewanalytics</a>"},{"pid":"9b3a5cf81a04efd542cee0c553584b77fef9ea00","tid":1507448,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY1A4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=4e0fcb6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"2a4c34a6d2881db8c877e73525a68b2c33f16586","t